        "description": "<p><strong>Source:</strong> Anime 5E Fifth Edition Core Rules, p. 181.</p><p><strong>Rules Summary:</strong> Indirect-contact disease spreads through air, contaminated objects, food or drink, or animal-to-person transfer. Treat airborne, contact, ingest, and injury vectors like the matching poison delivery categories when weaponised.</p>",
